- Server component is `async`; `searchParams` (and `params` for `[date]`) are Promises in Next 15 and MUST be `await`ed.
- Data fetched server-side via `createClient()` (cookie/RLS client from `@/lib/supabase/server`), plus server actions (`get...Action`) and/or a service class (`CashingUpService.getSessionByDateAndSite(supabase, ...)`). Actions return `{ success?, data?, error? }`-shaped objects; unwrap with `res.data ?? fallback`.
