Recommendation for a new recipient: follow the rota pattern — `process.env.YOUR_EMAIL ?? ''` as the default, and if operators may need to change it without a redeploy, layer a `system_settings` row on top with `(dbValue || envDefault)` precedence and skip sending (log a warning) when the resolved value is empty.
